   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 416,
   "width": 1790.19,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Both endpoints report to the manager on TCP 1514 with enrollment on 1515; the dashboard answers 443 and the API 55000. The existing UniFi Wazuh Ports group already allows only those two agent ports internally, so the re-enrollment needed no new rule and added no WAN exposure.",
   "originalText": "Both endpoints report to the manager on TCP 1514 with enrollment on 1515; the dashboard answers 443 and the API 55000. The existing UniFi Wazuh Ports group already allows only those two agent ports internally, so the re-enrollment needed no new rule and added no WAN exposure.",
   "fontSize": 12,
   "fontFamily": 5,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 11
  }
